Package com.application.tagging

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TagRepository
    Interface extension of a CrudRepository to be a repository for Tags.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RequestExistentTag
    Wrapper class on the information needed to indicate a Tag that already exists.
    RequestNewTag
    Wrapper class on the information needed to create a new tag.
    RequestTagApplication
    Wrapper class on the information needed to specify a pairing of Tag and SkillLevel.
    RequestUpdateTag
    Wrapper class on the information needed to update a Tag.
    Tag
    Entity for a tag so that available tags can be pre-specified.
    TagController
    Controller for performing operations on tags
    TagSkillLevelKey
    An embeddable key formed from the ids of a Post and a Tag.
